1
00:01:35,090 --> 00:01:38,250
[Episode 17]

2
00:01:38,250 --> 00:01:39,490
Yue Hua.

3
00:01:39,490 --> 00:01:41,010
I'm going to arrest Jing Yi Ming now.

4
00:01:41,010 --> 00:01:42,689
I'm afraid he'll destroy the evidence.

5
00:01:42,689 --> 00:01:46,927
Why don't you come with us
and witness his downfall?

6
00:01:47,927 --> 00:01:49,050
No.

7
00:01:49,050 --> 00:01:52,010
I have to return to Hanshui Palace
to report to Granny.

8
00:01:52,010 --> 00:01:54,031
Farewell.

9
00:02:04,850 --> 00:02:06,930
Yue Hua.

10
00:02:07,930 --> 00:02:09,409
Are you confused, Huo Xiao Mei?

11
00:02:09,409 --> 00:02:13,912
This Moon Envoy is actually
the Ding family's daughter, Ding Yue Hua.

12
00:02:35,489 --> 00:02:37,562
Shoot another signal.

13
00:03:07,090 --> 00:03:08,209
Zhang Yue.

14
00:03:08,209 --> 00:03:11,037
You still have unfinished business.

15
00:03:16,129 --> 00:03:18,649
Zhan is about to take over the Jing Mansion.

16
00:03:18,649 --> 00:03:22,170
Now is not the best time
to retrieve the Chang Hong Bi.

17
00:03:22,170 --> 00:03:24,530
I doubt the He Bo is out of tricks.

18
00:03:24,530 --> 00:03:28,209
While Zhan Zhao is fighting him,
that will be the best time.

19
00:03:29,209 --> 00:03:32,330
Zhang Yue,
if you don't bring back the Chang Hong Bi,

20
00:03:32,330 --> 00:03:35,150
your life will be forfeit.

21
00:03:44,209 --> 00:03:47,575
Master. Shao Ji Zu has sent two signals.

22
00:03:49,130 --> 00:03:51,850
Zhan Zhao will likely be here soon.

23
00:03:52,850 --> 00:03:54,850
Proceed as planned. Go, quickly!

24
00:03:54,850 --> 00:03:56,725
Yes, sir.

25
00:04:18,689 --> 00:04:20,290
Your martial arts have rusted for years.

26
00:04:20,290 --> 00:04:21,529
What trouble could you possibly cause?

27
00:04:21,529 --> 00:04:24,062
Your retribution is coming!

28
00:04:26,810 --> 00:04:28,082
Jing Yi Ming.

29
00:04:28,082 --> 00:04:31,010
Is this all you're capable of?

30
00:04:31,010 --> 00:04:32,850
You run Zhongxiao Pavilion,

31
00:04:32,850 --> 00:04:35,489
bullying defenseless young girls.

32
00:04:35,489 --> 00:04:38,530
You use Yemotian to control martial artists.

33
00:04:38,530 --> 00:04:40,330
With just this...

34
00:04:40,330 --> 00:04:43,909
you think you're fit to rule the world?

35
00:04:45,890 --> 00:04:49,289
You're just an arrogant, incompetent scoundrel!

36
00:04:49,289 --> 00:04:51,210
A complete hypocrite!

37
00:04:51,210 --> 00:04:53,250
- A despicable man!
- Shut up!

38
00:04:53,250 --> 00:04:56,625
You wench, you're stalling for time on purpose!

39
00:06:27,930 --> 00:06:29,103
- Madam!
- Madam!

40
00:06:29,103 --> 00:06:30,650
Quickly, move the unburned letters out of here!

41
00:06:30,650 --> 00:06:31,712
Put out the fire, now!

42
00:06:31,712 --> 00:06:32,775
Yes, sir!

43
00:06:32,775 --> 00:06:36,209
Zhan Zhao, you're still a step too late.

44
00:06:36,209 --> 00:06:41,362
What I've burned is enough to give me
leverage to negotiate with you.

45
00:07:04,449 --> 00:07:06,425
Ding.

46
00:07:11,290 --> 00:07:13,209
Be gentle.

47
00:07:14,209 --> 00:07:16,937
Don't hurt him again.

48
00:07:21,370 --> 00:07:22,529
Who are you looking for?

49
00:07:22,529 --> 00:07:23,636
I'm looking for Zhan Zhao.

50
00:07:23,636 --> 00:07:25,357
I have something important.

51
00:07:25,357 --> 00:07:26,810
Let her in.

52
00:07:26,810 --> 00:07:30,212
She helped us earlier at the Burial Mounds.

53
00:07:58,170 --> 00:08:01,075
Is there a child being held by the Jing family?

54
00:08:01,075 --> 00:08:02,329
Yes.

55
00:08:02,329 --> 00:08:05,750
The child is in the courtyard ahead.

56
00:08:08,890 --> 00:08:12,050
I'll deal with them. Hurry up.

57
00:08:22,930 --> 00:08:24,970
Xiao Di.

58
00:08:29,050 --> 00:08:32,330
Don't be afraid. I'm here to save you.

59
00:08:54,810 --> 00:08:56,750
Wait.

60
00:08:59,130 --> 00:09:00,890
Ding...

61
00:09:01,890 --> 00:09:03,708
He's not in good shape.

62
00:09:03,708 --> 00:09:06,187
Do you want to go see him?

63
00:09:25,028 --> 00:09:26,457
Where is he?

64
00:09:27,020 --> 00:09:28,649
We're a step too late.

65
00:09:28,649 --> 00:09:30,849
Zhan Zhao has already taken him.

66
00:09:31,610 --> 00:09:33,170
Zhang Ri.

67
00:09:33,170 --> 00:09:36,225
You're no match for Zhan Zhao
in a head-on confrontation.

68
00:09:37,969 --> 00:09:39,762
Go back first.

69
00:09:39,762 --> 00:09:41,490
Give me some time.

70
00:09:41,490 --> 00:09:44,425
I will definitely give Granny an explanation.

71
00:09:47,529 --> 00:09:49,230
Zhang Yue.

72
00:09:49,810 --> 00:09:51,685
Remember this.

73
00:09:52,290 --> 00:09:54,250
Without the Chang Hong Bi,

74
00:09:54,250 --> 00:09:57,525
you don't need to return to Hanshui Palace.

75
00:10:12,487 --> 00:10:15,615
[Soaring to the Heavens]

76
00:10:34,130 --> 00:10:35,370
This is the spring tea...

77
00:10:35,370 --> 00:10:38,889
I specially prepared for the birthday banquet.

78
00:10:38,889 --> 00:10:40,587
What a pity.

79
00:10:40,587 --> 00:10:42,887
It won't be needed anymore.

80
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:48,950
[Divine Longevity]

81
00:10:51,169 --> 00:10:53,850
Your end today was destined long ago.

82
00:10:53,850 --> 00:10:55,450
Say what you have to say quickly.

83
00:10:55,450 --> 00:10:57,130
Once you're done...

84
00:10:57,130 --> 00:11:00,210
it's time to move you to another place.

85
00:11:00,210 --> 00:11:02,712
Lord Zhan, you should understand.

86
00:11:02,712 --> 00:11:03,970
Even if you arrest me,

87
00:11:03,970 --> 00:11:07,200
you won't be able to close the case.

88
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,530
In the end,

89
00:11:08,530 --> 00:11:12,350
I'm just a pawn following orders.

90
00:11:12,350 --> 00:11:15,730
Why be so hard on me?

91
00:11:15,730 --> 00:11:18,210
Why not let me off the hook?

92
00:11:18,210 --> 00:11:20,250
With what I know,

93
00:11:20,250 --> 00:11:22,682
I can help you clear the fog.

94
00:11:22,682 --> 00:11:23,970
When that happens,

95
00:11:23,970 --> 00:11:25,690
promotions and rewards

96
00:11:25,690 --> 00:11:28,090
will be easily within your reach.

97
00:11:28,090 --> 00:11:29,589
As for your fate,

98
00:11:29,589 --> 00:11:31,369
the law will decide it.

99
00:11:31,369 --> 00:11:33,129
Even if you wish to redeem yourself,

100
00:11:33,129 --> 00:11:34,889
it depends on the crimes you've committed.

101
00:11:34,889 --> 00:11:37,249
You ran Zhongxiao Pavilion and controlled
martial artists.

102
00:11:37,249 --> 00:11:39,067
You've committed all sorts of evil deeds.

103
00:11:39,067 --> 00:11:40,210
If you were allowed to live,

104
00:11:40,210 --> 00:11:44,200
to those young girls you violated
and the innocents who died because of you,

105
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:47,170
wouldn't that be a grave injustice?

106
00:11:47,170 --> 00:11:50,649
It seems that deep down,
you are still a chivalrous hero.

107
00:11:50,649 --> 00:11:54,489
But with your personality,
I'm afraid you'll suffer for it in the court.

108
00:11:54,489 --> 00:11:57,369
You have only uncovered
a corner of the conspiracy.

109
00:11:57,369 --> 00:11:59,330
And you're so impatient now.

110
00:11:59,330 --> 00:12:04,009
A case this big is not something you
or Kaifeng Prefecture can decide alone.

111
00:12:04,009 --> 00:12:07,330
I have plenty of opportunities
to negotiate with others.

112
00:12:07,330 --> 00:12:12,925
When the time comes, don't blame me
for not giving you a chance for promotion.

113
00:12:15,009 --> 00:12:17,000
Not necessarily.

114
00:12:19,930 --> 00:12:23,090
If I find out what your bargaining chip is,

115
00:12:23,090 --> 00:12:25,617
you'll have no reason to stay alive.

116
00:12:26,825 --> 00:12:28,350
Fine!

117
00:12:28,350 --> 00:12:30,155
Then I shall wait and see.

118
00:12:30,155 --> 00:12:34,712
Let's see what you can find
from that room full of ashes!

119
00:12:44,749 --> 00:12:45,850
Xiao Di,

120
00:12:45,850 --> 00:12:48,240
we finally meet again.

121
00:12:51,690 --> 00:12:53,050
In a few more days,

122
00:12:53,050 --> 00:12:54,810
the scent of medicine will fade away.

123
00:12:54,810 --> 00:12:57,737
You'll be just like any other child.

124
00:12:59,969 --> 00:13:02,091
Where is Zhao Hui?

125
00:13:03,570 --> 00:13:05,290
Ding...

126
00:13:05,290 --> 00:13:07,425
He is badly injured.

127
00:13:14,450 --> 00:13:18,290
The Great Compassion Palm has damaged
his meridians and internal organs.

128
00:13:18,290 --> 00:13:19,490
For now,

129
00:13:19,490 --> 00:13:22,330
we can only use our inner power
to treat his injuries.

130
00:13:22,330 --> 00:13:24,876
But even this may not be effective.

131
00:13:25,889 --> 00:13:27,050
Yue Hua.

132
00:13:27,050 --> 00:13:29,690
For the time being,
you should stay by his side.

133
00:13:29,690 --> 00:13:31,700
In case...

134
00:13:44,249 --> 00:13:46,163
Is there any Linglong Honey left?

135
00:13:47,930 --> 00:13:49,962
Only two pills left.

136
00:13:51,650 --> 00:13:53,860
This has a miraculous effect on pain.

137
00:13:53,860 --> 00:13:57,649
It can help Ding won't be so hard to endure.

138
00:13:58,570 --> 00:14:00,450
Thank you.

139
00:14:27,769 --> 00:14:29,090
Lord Zhan.

140
00:14:29,090 --> 00:14:32,369
The items we saved this time are correspondence
between He Bo and Western Xia.

141
00:14:32,369 --> 00:14:33,610
With these,

142
00:14:33,610 --> 00:14:35,249
your name can finally be cleared.

143
00:14:35,249 --> 00:14:36,969
Unfortunately...

144
00:14:36,969 --> 00:14:40,410
these letters don't involve
the master behind He Bo.

145
00:14:40,410 --> 00:14:41,769
Previously,

146
00:14:41,769 --> 00:14:44,950
the Zhongxiao Pavilion ledgers mentioned
by the Yicheng Magistrate...

147
00:14:44,950 --> 00:14:47,437
were also destroyed.

148
00:14:51,489 --> 00:14:52,810
Commander Meng.

149
00:14:52,810 --> 00:14:54,769
When will you escort
Jing Yi Ming back to the capital?

150
00:14:54,769 --> 00:14:56,170
We set off in two days.

151
00:14:56,170 --> 00:14:57,530
The evidence still needs to be inventoried.

152
00:14:57,530 --> 00:14:58,609
The witnesses...

153
00:14:58,609 --> 00:14:59,769
also need some time to recover.

154
00:14:59,769 --> 00:15:01,450
Leave the evidence to me.

155
00:15:01,450 --> 00:15:03,610
I'll leave the suspects' statements to you.

156
00:15:03,610 --> 00:15:05,330
Alright, don't worry.

157
00:15:05,330 --> 00:15:09,210
As you requested, the suspects
from Zhongxiao Pavilion have been separated.

158
00:15:09,210 --> 00:15:10,729
So they won't be colluding.

159
00:15:10,729 --> 00:15:13,762
We can start the interrogations tonight.

160
00:15:33,050 --> 00:15:34,170
Zhan.

161
00:15:34,170 --> 00:15:36,437
Why aren't you eating?

162
00:15:37,769 --> 00:15:40,237
I haven't finished organizing yet.

163
00:15:53,930 --> 00:15:57,012
What terms did He Bo try to negotiate?

164
00:16:01,849 --> 00:16:03,850
He wanted to use the letters he burned

165
00:16:03,850 --> 00:16:07,090
to bargain for his own immunity in this case.

166
00:16:07,090 --> 00:16:09,175
I want to look for more clues.

167
00:16:09,175 --> 00:16:12,125
I won't give him any chance to survive.

168
00:16:14,210 --> 00:16:15,690
Then I'll help you look.

169
00:16:15,690 --> 00:16:17,729
You should eat something before that.

170
00:16:17,729 --> 00:16:20,525
Otherwise, you won't have the energy to work.

171
00:16:23,450 --> 00:16:25,187
Try some.

172
00:16:49,849 --> 00:16:51,410
Miss Huo.

173
00:16:51,410 --> 00:16:53,800
I can return this to its owner now.

174
00:16:59,249 --> 00:17:01,530
I noticed the cord on this jade ring
is quite exquisite.

175
00:17:01,530 --> 00:17:03,769
It's tied into a peace knot.

176
00:17:03,769 --> 00:17:05,530
If I'm not mistaken,

177
00:17:05,530 --> 00:17:07,450
it must be from Yuan'an Temple, right?

178
00:17:07,450 --> 00:17:09,925
My aunt gave it to me.

179
00:17:09,925 --> 00:17:11,729
She said...

180
00:17:11,729 --> 00:17:14,262
it would keep me safe.

181
00:17:20,450 --> 00:17:23,412
I remember being very
frail and sickly as a child.

182
00:17:23,412 --> 00:17:26,129
Once, I fell so seriously ill.

183
00:17:26,129 --> 00:17:28,217
It almost cost me my life.

184
00:17:28,217 --> 00:17:29,938
Since I've started carrying this,

185
00:17:29,938 --> 00:17:32,825
I've really become much healthier.

186
00:17:36,369 --> 00:17:37,570
Huo Xiao Mei.

187
00:17:37,570 --> 00:17:41,129
You're saving all the good things
for your Zhan, aren't you?

188
00:17:42,129 --> 00:17:43,890
Not only are you whispering behind my back,

189
00:17:43,890 --> 00:17:46,530
but you're also eating alone without me.

190
00:17:46,530 --> 00:17:48,009
You didn't come here late at night

191
00:17:48,009 --> 00:17:49,770
just for these two pastries, did you?

192
00:17:49,770 --> 00:17:51,290
How dare you say that?

193
00:17:51,290 --> 00:17:52,530
If I hadn't asked Ming Zhu,

194
00:17:52,530 --> 00:17:54,729
I wouldn't have known you were
trying to handle things yourself again.

195
00:17:54,729 --> 00:17:56,330
The room is a total mess.

196
00:17:56,330 --> 00:17:59,050
If you work alone, you'll be at it until dawn.

197
00:17:59,050 --> 00:18:00,690
So much for my good intentions.

198
00:18:00,690 --> 00:18:03,810
I should've just gone to bed!

199
00:18:04,889 --> 00:18:08,290
Those two fellas will come here after
securing the Chang Hong Bi.

200
00:18:08,290 --> 00:18:10,170
I'm afraid this secret room is too small.

201
00:18:10,170 --> 00:18:14,200
Why don't we let Jing Yi Ming's
'honored guests' make some space for us?

202
00:18:21,249 --> 00:18:23,562
Don't scare me.

203
00:18:25,930 --> 00:18:28,862
Let's go, let's go. Hurry up.

204
00:19:26,810 --> 00:19:28,263
Look at the time.

205
00:19:28,263 --> 00:19:30,209
You're still in the mood
to organize the case files.

206
00:19:30,209 --> 00:19:33,050
That He Bo has no sense of danger.

207
00:19:33,050 --> 00:19:35,330
We should make a move now.

208
00:19:36,330 --> 00:19:38,116
The Zhongxiao Pavilion case

209
00:19:38,116 --> 00:19:40,010
didn't implicate you.

210
00:19:40,010 --> 00:19:42,330
But if you act now,

211
00:19:42,330 --> 00:19:45,449
you'll be delivering yourself to them.

212
00:19:45,449 --> 00:19:47,290
The destruction of Zhongxiao Pavilion

213
00:19:47,290 --> 00:19:50,925
is a significant blow
to His Lordship's great cause.

214
00:19:50,925 --> 00:19:52,970
I will report this matter myself.

215
00:19:52,970 --> 00:19:56,970
Whatever the punishment, I will bear it alone.

216
00:19:56,970 --> 00:20:01,369
He Bo won't be so stupid
as to confess everything to Zhan Zhao.

217
00:20:01,369 --> 00:20:05,825
Besides, he knows very little.
He can't see the whole picture.

218
00:20:05,825 --> 00:20:09,209
Let's see what Zhan Zhao can actually find out.

219
00:20:09,209 --> 00:20:11,330
If he finds nothing in the end,

220
00:20:11,330 --> 00:20:12,770
that would be for the best.

221
00:20:12,770 --> 00:20:14,530
And what if he does find something?

222
00:20:14,530 --> 00:20:18,530
Even if he does, there's no need to panic.

223
00:20:18,530 --> 00:20:20,770
Whose life will be difficult then

224
00:20:20,770 --> 00:20:23,168
is yet to be determined.

225
00:21:32,970 --> 00:21:34,787
Look at this.

226
00:21:34,787 --> 00:21:39,250
This seal pattern is the same
as the one on Clerk Fang's token.

227
00:21:39,250 --> 00:21:44,050
It seems this seal and the tokens held
by the officials correspond to each other.

228
00:21:44,050 --> 00:21:49,610
Each of these books records the token owner's
visits to Zhongxiao Pavilion and expenses.

229
00:21:49,610 --> 00:21:51,382
But there are no names of the officials.

230
00:21:51,382 --> 00:21:55,889
He Bo must have another official roster
that matches the seal patterns.

231
00:21:55,889 --> 00:21:57,210
We've been busy all night,

232
00:21:57,210 --> 00:21:59,915
but haven't found a single clue
about the roster.

233
00:21:59,915 --> 00:22:01,609
Is the heavens blind?

234
00:22:01,609 --> 00:22:03,730
A fire helped him burn everything.

235
00:22:03,730 --> 00:22:06,216
Then the things we sorted out all night

236
00:22:06,216 --> 00:22:07,782
are just a bunch of useless papers.

237
00:22:07,782 --> 00:22:09,987
They are of no use.

238
00:22:11,409 --> 00:22:12,849
What if...

239
00:22:12,849 --> 00:22:14,742
we ask the girls from Zhongxiao Pavilion
to identify them?

240
00:22:14,742 --> 00:22:17,600
They've never seen the officials' faces.

241
00:22:20,250 --> 00:22:22,525
I also found these.

242
00:22:27,169 --> 00:22:30,262
These are letters between He Bo and others.

243
00:22:30,262 --> 00:22:33,290
The signatures are the writers' seals.

244
00:22:33,290 --> 00:22:35,290
These seals are all different.

245
00:22:35,290 --> 00:22:38,250
They are very different from the seal patterns
in the previous books.

246
00:22:38,250 --> 00:22:42,275
They should represent different subordinates
of Lord of Xiangyang.

247
00:22:45,490 --> 00:22:48,437
The design of these seals follows a pattern.

248
00:22:48,437 --> 00:22:49,770
Perhaps if we piece them together,

249
00:22:49,770 --> 00:22:52,330
we can get a complete symbol or pattern.

250
00:22:52,330 --> 00:22:53,970
We can't.

251
00:22:53,970 --> 00:22:56,689
These seals were either burned...

252
00:22:56,689 --> 00:22:59,175
or soaked in water.

253
00:23:12,849 --> 00:23:14,770
We haven't reached a dead end yet.

254
00:23:14,770 --> 00:23:15,820
It's been all night.

255
00:23:15,820 --> 00:23:17,169
You've all worked hard.

256
00:23:17,169 --> 00:23:19,575
Go back to the inn and rest first.

257
00:23:21,409 --> 00:23:23,325
I'm fine.

258
00:23:23,325 --> 00:23:26,437
Miss Huo, take them back.

259
00:23:28,090 --> 00:23:30,050
I'll go check on Zhao Hui.

260
00:23:30,050 --> 00:23:31,090
I'll keep an eye on him.

261
00:23:31,090 --> 00:23:33,125
Don't worry.

262
00:23:36,849 --> 00:23:38,600
Go ahead.

263
00:24:11,250 --> 00:24:13,570
We got absolutely nothing from tonight.

264
00:24:13,570 --> 00:24:16,449
The Tang Sect insists that this has
nothing to do with Shao Ji Zu.

265
00:24:16,449 --> 00:24:18,810
That Zhi Hua is even more
of a tough nut to crack.

266
00:24:18,810 --> 00:24:20,530
Completely uncooperative!

267
00:24:20,530 --> 00:24:22,369
He said he's doomed to die anyway.

268
00:24:22,369 --> 00:24:24,950
It's just a matter of time
before the axe falls.

269
00:24:36,810 --> 00:24:39,400
Is Ding feeling any better?

270
00:24:42,409 --> 00:24:43,610
You should get some rest too.

271
00:24:43,610 --> 00:24:45,758
I'm going to the Jing Mansion.

272
00:25:08,010 --> 00:25:11,169
Bai, what are you doing?

273
00:25:11,169 --> 00:25:12,689
Let me ask you.

274
00:25:12,689 --> 00:25:14,490
Aren't you one of the Prince's men?

275
00:25:14,490 --> 00:25:17,490
If the Guanghua Army meets you,
wouldn't they have to show you respect?

276
00:25:17,490 --> 00:25:19,090
Naturally.

277
00:25:19,090 --> 00:25:20,236
Good.

278
00:25:20,236 --> 00:25:21,810
Take me to the prison.

279
00:25:21,810 --> 00:25:22,890
What are you planning?

280
00:25:22,890 --> 00:25:24,794
To help your Lord, of course.

281
00:25:24,794 --> 00:25:27,090
To deal with a shameless man like Zhi Hua,

282
00:25:27,090 --> 00:25:29,837
I have better methods than the officials.

283
00:26:49,090 --> 00:26:51,187
Zhan.

284
00:26:53,930 --> 00:26:56,476
Some things are simply fate.

285
00:26:56,476 --> 00:26:57,678
You've already done your best.

286
00:26:57,678 --> 00:26:59,900
Success depends on human effort.

287
00:26:59,900 --> 00:27:03,287
Miss Huo, go back and get some rest.

288
00:28:22,050 --> 00:28:24,812
Bai, what's wrong?

289
00:29:19,849 --> 00:29:21,490
If I'm not mistaken,

290
00:29:21,490 --> 00:29:23,123
this seal at the bottom

291
00:29:23,123 --> 00:29:25,169
represents Lord of Xiangyang.

292
00:29:25,169 --> 00:29:29,207
The four around it represent
his four different subordinates.

293
00:29:30,409 --> 00:29:32,312
Look at this.

294
00:29:34,369 --> 00:29:36,449
The letters found in He Bo's residence.

295
00:29:36,449 --> 00:29:38,490
It must have been written to him by others.

296
00:29:38,490 --> 00:29:39,930
Among these letters,

297
00:29:39,930 --> 00:29:42,287
there are these three types of seals.

298
00:29:44,449 --> 00:29:45,730
By this logic,

299
00:29:45,730 --> 00:29:47,650
the seal for this empty spot

300
00:29:47,650 --> 00:29:49,143
belongs to He Bo.

301
00:29:49,143 --> 00:29:51,010
But look.

302
00:29:51,010 --> 00:29:53,810
The seal on this ledger.

303
00:29:53,810 --> 00:29:55,850
It is exactly the same as the seal

304
00:29:55,850 --> 00:29:58,290
in the top right corner.

305
00:30:00,449 --> 00:30:04,395
We previously deduced
that these ledgers were compiled by He Bo.

306
00:30:04,395 --> 00:30:06,610
But the seal on this ledger

307
00:30:06,610 --> 00:30:08,358
does not belong to He Bo.

308
00:30:08,358 --> 00:30:09,605
It seems...

309
00:30:09,605 --> 00:30:12,449
that there was another person involved
in the management of Zhongxiao Pavilion.

310
00:30:12,449 --> 00:30:14,690
Exactly.

311
00:30:14,690 --> 00:30:18,690
Perhaps the roster of officials wasn't burned.

312
00:30:18,690 --> 00:30:21,400
Instead, it was never in He Bo's hands.

313
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:24,412
That explains my previous confusion.

314
00:30:24,412 --> 00:30:26,570
He Bo is a man living outside the world.

315
00:30:26,570 --> 00:30:29,625
How could he be so deeply
involved with officialdom?

316
00:30:30,209 --> 00:30:34,530
Zhan. It seems the one using Zhongxiao Pavilion
to control officials...

317
00:30:34,530 --> 00:30:36,637
is someone else.

318
00:30:39,490 --> 00:30:41,595
We'll have to ask Zhi Hua.

319
00:30:41,595 --> 00:30:43,609
Lord Zhan.

320
00:30:43,609 --> 00:30:46,112
Lord Zhan, something happened!

321
00:31:17,929 --> 00:31:19,250
Why did you save him?

322
00:31:19,250 --> 00:31:21,129
He killed Zhao Zhi Er and Ming Zhu Er.

323
00:31:21,129 --> 00:31:24,437
Bai, what are you saying?

324
00:31:31,290 --> 00:31:33,412
Bai.

325
00:31:37,970 --> 00:31:39,837
Bai.

326
00:31:51,090 --> 00:31:53,037
What did you see?

327
00:31:53,037 --> 00:31:54,609
Are you seeing hallucinations again?

328
00:31:54,609 --> 00:31:57,589
That day in the forest,
you weren't acting when you fought Zhi Hua.

329
00:31:57,589 --> 00:31:58,712
You were really poisoned.

330
00:31:58,712 --> 00:31:59,770
I wasn't.

331
00:31:59,770 --> 00:32:02,369
Even if Zhi Hua didn't kill
Zhao Zhi Er and Ming Zhu Er,

332
00:32:02,369 --> 00:32:04,275
he is still heinous and deserves to die.

333
00:32:04,275 --> 00:32:05,530
He harmed so many people.

334
00:32:05,530 --> 00:32:09,369
But in the hands of the law,
he'll just be executed once.

335
00:32:09,369 --> 00:32:12,490
Letting him die just once is too good for him.

336
00:32:12,490 --> 00:32:14,997
In my hands,
I can make him die a thousand times over!

337
00:32:14,997 --> 00:32:16,929
Not just him, but Jing Yi Ming too.

338
00:32:16,929 --> 00:32:20,601
All the accomplices of Zhongxiao Pavilion
should be tortured to death!

339
00:32:21,169 --> 00:32:22,490
Bai Yu Tang!

340
00:32:22,490 --> 00:32:24,369
What you're seeing now are hallucinations.

341
00:32:24,369 --> 00:32:25,810
Snap out of it.

342
00:32:25,810 --> 00:32:28,243
Listen to me. Zhi Hua cannot die yet.

343
00:32:28,243 --> 00:32:31,162
There are things I must ask him.

344
00:32:40,889 --> 00:32:43,025
I went to see Zhi Hua earlier...

345
00:32:43,025 --> 00:32:45,400
to make him talk.

346
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:47,625
To help you.

347
00:32:49,530 --> 00:32:50,970
Don't worry.

348
00:32:50,970 --> 00:32:53,387
Leave the rest to me.

349
00:32:56,963 --> 00:33:00,050
I won't say a word.

350
00:33:00,050 --> 00:33:02,570
Using my life as a stepping stone...

351
00:33:02,570 --> 00:33:05,387
for your promotion and titles?

352
00:33:07,770 --> 00:33:09,530
In your dreams.

353
00:33:09,530 --> 00:33:12,649
I don't care about promotions or titles.

354
00:33:12,649 --> 00:33:14,649
But if you don't say anything...

355
00:33:14,649 --> 00:33:17,010
someone else will benefit from it.

356
00:33:17,010 --> 00:33:20,448
Like the person who wants you dead.

357
00:33:21,010 --> 00:33:24,929
You know I'm not talking about Shao Ji Zu.

358
00:33:25,929 --> 00:33:27,689
Among Lord of Xiangyang's men,

359
00:33:27,689 --> 00:33:31,200
one person co-managed Zhongxiao Pavilion
with He Bo.

360
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:34,010
But he wasn't involved in this case.

361
00:33:34,010 --> 00:33:37,470
He had no reason to go to such lengths
to kill you.

362
00:33:38,330 --> 00:33:40,730
If you think about it, you'll understand.

363
00:33:40,730 --> 00:33:42,890
The person who suspected Hanshui Palace

364
00:33:42,890 --> 00:33:45,129
and was ruthless enough

365
00:33:45,129 --> 00:33:49,252
to want to silence you and the
Shangqing disciples together...

366
00:33:49,929 --> 00:33:52,850
could only be Jing Yi Ming.

367
00:33:55,810 --> 00:33:57,849
Your Great Compassion Palm...

368
00:33:57,849 --> 00:34:00,512
was taught to you by Jing Yi Ming, right?

369
00:34:03,250 --> 00:34:05,449
You're full of hatred for his eldest son.

370
00:34:05,449 --> 00:34:07,849
Combined with Jing Yi Ming's philandering,

371
00:34:07,849 --> 00:34:11,250
it made me realize your true identity.

372
00:34:13,849 --> 00:34:15,929
Even a tiger doesn't eat its cub.

373
00:34:15,929 --> 00:34:19,907
I truly feel sorry
for your loyalty and filial piety.

374
00:34:20,490 --> 00:34:22,689
He taught you the Great Compassion Palm,

375
00:34:22,689 --> 00:34:24,849
giving you a glimmer of hope.

376
00:34:24,849 --> 00:34:29,530
You thought that one day,
he would publicly acknowledge you.

377
00:34:29,530 --> 00:34:31,050
But what is the reality?

378
00:34:31,050 --> 00:34:34,570
He taught you martial arts
only so you would risk your life for him.

379
00:34:34,570 --> 00:34:35,889
To him,

380
00:34:35,889 --> 00:34:40,100
you are just his most loyal
and useful death soldier.

381
00:34:41,100 --> 00:34:42,449
Yesterday,

382
00:34:42,449 --> 00:34:45,090
he pinned all the blame on you.

383
00:34:45,090 --> 00:34:46,730
He wanted to use that...

384
00:34:46,730 --> 00:34:49,277
to clear himself.

385
00:34:50,169 --> 00:34:52,930
The evidence of his crimes...

386
00:34:52,930 --> 00:34:55,689
is all laid out right there.

387
00:34:55,689 --> 00:34:57,689
The evidence is irrefutable.

388
00:34:57,689 --> 00:34:59,369
How can he get away with it?

389
00:34:59,369 --> 00:35:02,209
By providing important clues.

390
00:35:03,209 --> 00:35:07,609
The Jing family's ledgers and letters
were all burned by him.

391
00:35:07,609 --> 00:35:09,929
He offered to reveal the details,

392
00:35:09,929 --> 00:35:11,330
and in exchange...

393
00:35:11,330 --> 00:35:14,150
for a chance to live.

394
00:35:20,929 --> 00:35:22,770
I don't want to see him go free,

395
00:35:22,770 --> 00:35:24,849
but I have no other choice.

396
00:35:24,849 --> 00:35:26,409
If he hadn't spoken up,

397
00:35:26,409 --> 00:35:28,369
we would never have known

398
00:35:28,369 --> 00:35:30,929
that Zhongxiao Pavilion was a joint venture.

399
00:35:30,929 --> 00:35:32,570
After giving us the clues,

400
00:35:32,570 --> 00:35:34,449
he denied everything he could,

401
00:35:34,449 --> 00:35:37,475
pinning all the guilt on you.

402
00:35:37,475 --> 00:35:39,449
If this continues,

403
00:35:39,449 --> 00:35:40,889
I'm afraid...

404
00:35:40,889 --> 00:35:43,737
he really will get away with it.

405
00:35:43,737 --> 00:35:46,562
Reveal the details?

406
00:35:47,970 --> 00:35:50,769
What details...

407
00:35:50,769 --> 00:35:53,612
will he understand?

408
00:36:29,570 --> 00:36:32,130
Lord Zhan.

409
00:36:35,249 --> 00:36:37,810
You've finally come around.

410
00:36:38,625 --> 00:36:42,010
I don't ask for much.

411
00:36:42,010 --> 00:36:45,387
I just want to stay alive.

412
00:36:51,249 --> 00:36:53,769
Under Lord of Xiangyang,
there are Four Divine Lords.

413
00:36:53,769 --> 00:36:54,970
He Bo,

414
00:36:54,970 --> 00:36:56,410
Si Ming,

415
00:36:56,410 --> 00:36:57,450
Dong Jun,

416
00:36:57,450 --> 00:36:59,287
Shan Gui.

417
00:36:59,287 --> 00:37:00,850
Among them,

418
00:37:00,850 --> 00:37:04,130
Si Ming and you
run Zhongxiao Pavilion together.

419
00:37:04,130 --> 00:37:07,649
You only wanted to use Zhongxiao Pavilion
to manipulate martial artists.

420
00:37:07,649 --> 00:37:12,189
The one who uncovered the officials' true
identities and used that to control them...

421
00:37:12,189 --> 00:37:13,850
was Si Ming.

422
00:37:13,850 --> 00:37:18,404
The secrets you can use to negotiate
with the government are only these.

423
00:37:18,404 --> 00:37:20,969
And you only know this much.

424
00:37:21,570 --> 00:37:24,263
Lord of Xiangyang is wary
of the Four Divine Lords.

425
00:37:24,263 --> 00:37:26,649
He doesn't let you have much contact.

426
00:37:26,649 --> 00:37:30,249
He's worried that if one is caught,
the others will be implicated.

427
00:37:30,249 --> 00:37:34,090
So he only lets you exchange letters.

428
00:37:34,090 --> 00:37:37,410
Offering to confess is just putting on a show.

429
00:37:37,410 --> 00:37:40,850
You're nothing more than fabricating clues.

430
00:37:40,850 --> 00:37:43,575
Deceiving the government.

431
00:37:49,810 --> 00:37:51,729
I came here...

432
00:37:51,729 --> 00:37:55,437
just to see you in this state!

433
00:37:56,729 --> 00:37:59,169
I cannot make a scum like you...

434
00:37:59,169 --> 00:38:00,609
feel remorse for Liu Hong Yi,

435
00:38:00,609 --> 00:38:01,970
Fan Zhong Yu,

436
00:38:01,970 --> 00:38:06,776
the Ding family, the women of
Zhongxiao Pavilion, and the martial artists.

437
00:38:06,776 --> 00:38:08,850
But I can extinguish your hope!

438
00:38:08,850 --> 00:38:10,970
Leaving you with only despair...

439
00:38:10,970 --> 00:38:13,362
and fear.

440
00:38:18,490 --> 00:38:22,769
This can be considered
a small consolation to those victims.

441
00:38:23,650 --> 00:38:25,930
Don't even think about a quick death.

442
00:38:25,930 --> 00:38:29,050
The law has its own procedures.

443
00:38:29,050 --> 00:38:31,329
You will spend day after day...

444
00:38:31,329 --> 00:38:33,450
day after day...

445
00:38:33,450 --> 00:38:36,250
suffering in this prison.

446
00:38:39,810 --> 00:38:40,873
Lord Zhan!

447
00:38:40,873 --> 00:38:42,689
By the way,

448
00:38:42,689 --> 00:38:44,850
everything regarding Zhongxiao Pavilion,

449
00:38:44,850 --> 00:38:47,289
someone has already confessed clearly.

450
00:38:47,289 --> 00:38:49,129
I won't trouble He Bo,

451
00:38:49,129 --> 00:38:51,467
to speak any further.

452
00:38:52,689 --> 00:38:55,462
To the Imperial Court,

453
00:38:55,462 --> 00:38:58,350
you are no longer of any use.

454
00:39:20,875 --> 00:39:22,625
[I, Zhi Hua,
truthfully confess all the above statements]

455
00:39:29,729 --> 00:39:32,087
Have you ever seen Si Ming?

456
00:39:35,170 --> 00:39:37,170
No.

457
00:39:37,170 --> 00:39:38,850
He acts with great caution.

458
00:39:38,850 --> 00:39:41,370
His orders are mostly passed
to me through others.

459
00:39:41,370 --> 00:39:43,650
I have never seen him.

460
00:39:46,209 --> 00:39:47,930
There is one more thing...

461
00:39:47,930 --> 00:39:50,350
I would like to ask you.

462
00:40:03,769 --> 00:40:05,850
Father.

463
00:40:06,850 --> 00:40:09,000
Father.

464
00:40:11,010 --> 00:40:13,250
I was the one who asked Zhan Zhao...

465
00:40:13,250 --> 00:40:15,050
to place us

466
00:40:15,050 --> 00:40:17,462
in the same cell.

467
00:40:17,462 --> 00:40:20,050
Because I wanted to tell you personally.

468
00:40:20,050 --> 00:40:21,812
It was I...

469
00:40:21,812 --> 00:40:24,289
who betrayed you.

470
00:40:24,289 --> 00:40:27,570
I personally cut off your escape route.

471
00:40:27,570 --> 00:40:29,956
And there is one more thing, I...

472
00:40:29,956 --> 00:40:32,375
I want to tell you.

473
00:40:34,890 --> 00:40:39,000
That precious son of yours
whom you wanted to pass your legacy to...

474
00:40:42,925 --> 00:40:45,809
I killed him too.

475
00:40:46,809 --> 00:40:50,087
I killed him with my own hands.

476
00:41:41,090 --> 00:41:43,087
Zhan.

477
00:41:49,090 --> 00:41:50,556
I'll take care of him here.

478
00:41:50,556 --> 00:41:52,010
You've worked hard on the case.

479
00:41:52,010 --> 00:41:54,010
Get some rest while you can.

480
00:41:54,010 --> 00:41:56,000
It's no matter.

481
00:42:03,450 --> 00:42:05,289
Your trip to the Jing Mansion...

482
00:42:05,289 --> 00:42:07,570
was for the Chang Hong Bi?

483
00:42:08,570 --> 00:42:10,210
If you don't bring it back,

484
00:42:10,210 --> 00:42:13,106
Granny Hanshui won't forgive you easily.

485
00:42:13,689 --> 00:42:15,769
Have you thought of how to handle it?

486
00:42:15,769 --> 00:42:18,010
I haven't thought of a plan yet.

487
00:42:18,010 --> 00:42:19,609
But I know,

488
00:42:19,609 --> 00:42:22,050
I've made too many mistakes before.

489
00:42:22,050 --> 00:42:24,512
I don't want to keep making them.

490
00:42:28,970 --> 00:42:32,100
You can't return to Hanshui Palace.

491
00:42:34,010 --> 00:42:36,052
Go home.

492
00:42:37,010 --> 00:42:40,375
The evidence of Jing Yi Ming's crimes
is as solid as a mountain.

493
00:42:40,375 --> 00:42:43,010
Lord Bao will surely bring justice
to the Ding family.

494
00:42:43,010 --> 00:42:44,912
In other words,

495
00:42:44,912 --> 00:42:46,450
he will certainly face the death penalty.

496
00:42:46,450 --> 00:42:48,060
Yes.

497
00:42:48,689 --> 00:42:50,209
When I was at the Ding family,

498
00:42:50,209 --> 00:42:52,729
Zhao Hui spoke to me about Xiao Yun.

499
00:42:52,729 --> 00:42:54,250
He deeply regretted

500
00:42:54,250 --> 00:42:56,129
not believing you at the time.

501
00:42:56,129 --> 00:42:57,809
After you left home,

502
00:42:57,809 --> 00:43:00,050
he's been keeping Xiao Yun's body.

503
00:43:00,050 --> 00:43:02,129
He hoped you'd return to find evidence.

504
00:43:02,129 --> 00:43:05,012
Seek justice for Xiao Yun.
